      "text": "We provide tools and sustainable hosting so that each local festival can have it’s own website and mobile app. Together with online training materials and centralised production support we aim to encourage local organisations, radio stations and individuals to start local festivals in their area. The combination of these tools will be designed to make it as simple as possible to create a sustainable local festival.\n"
