      "text": "During the summer we will be creating a mobile application which allows an organiser to take photos and short community advertisements from local businesses taking part in the festival. The mobile application geolocates the photographs automatically creating a festival map of participating venues for the web site and festival programme.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "f092057c7b955282",
      "text": "The app will explain how the festival works, and be customisable with local images, stories and oral history. The content gathered by this app can be used to create a local festival app, which can be co-produced with people from the community. This way each local festival can have it’s own app, providing a number of training opportunities for people in the area.\n"
